{"tid":2408465,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港府擬修例 銀行須嚴審內地官賬戶","createTime":"2021-02-15T03:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T03:52:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"500f0887f5a9fdc2e141436e87033586ad853a22","tid":2408465,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:39:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210215/YLK7DX5LMBE3TFMOHDWT6NZQPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210215%2FYLK7DX5LMBE3TFMOHDWT6NZQPY%2F&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eaZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=56aee96d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210215%2FYLK7DX5LMBE3TFMOHDWT6NZQPY%2F&h=9584e29a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210215/YLK7DX5LMBE3TFMOHDWT6NZQPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n港府擬修例 銀行須嚴審內地官賬戶<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】財庫局早前發出諮詢文件，根據財務行動特別組織（特別組織）的建議修訂《打擊洗錢條例》（下稱條例），包括將內地官員納入需要更嚴格客戶盡職審查的外地政治人物（Politically Exposed Persons, PEPs）類別，意味未來將對內地官員的銀行賬戶交易，作出更嚴格的反洗錢審查。有分析認為，有關修訂是防止香港成為走資基地，但或令銀行「更加唔夠膽做生意」，對業務有打擊。<br />\n<br />\n特別組織是制訂打擊洗錢及恐怖分子資金籌集國際標準的跨政府組織，成員包括全球39個主要經濟體。所謂「PEP」，是根據國際準則及本地監管制訂的《打擊洗錢及恐怖分子資金籌集指引》內的規訂，認可機構須對所有客戶進行。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MW2sjX32-n5a7Snut8ZJI-8Vg3U=/7846x5231/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6UXNGDLKKJHW3HP7RV2VQ3WBR4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMW2sjX32-n5a7Snut8ZJI-8Vg3U%3D%2F7846x5231%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6UXNGDLKKJHW3HP7RV2VQ3WBR4.jpg&h=866be1e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有分析認為有關修訂是防止香港成為走資基地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n業界：定義更清晰<br />\n<br />\n據政府新聞網，有關諮詢去年11月公佈。。。。。。。。，並建議適用於前政治人物。<br />\n<br />\n有本地銀行業界指出，現時每。。。。。。。。，確保每間銀行都要按標準執行。<br />\n<br />\n《金融時報》引述孖士打律師行合夥人李顯能（Alan Linning）指出，該。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國克林信大學經濟系副教授徐家健表示，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"2373167147ab6da9d7d3bf301dd803ba04d94542","tid":2408465,"uid":144453,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yBoFwvg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyBoFwvg.gif&h=8cbdf0bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b3c4901333b1be0e83107a90e1e954bc7f24105","tid":2408465,"uid":267167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"外地政治人物？搞港獨？"},{"pid":"eaa54a9d55ab686acaec3844fb7ad3a71b59cddf","tid":2408465,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:43:07.000Z","msg":"走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6836476f7d3964a94f444b7eb6939bf256f46c9a","tid":2408465,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:43:35.000Z","msg":"內地？ 黃大仙呀？"},{"pid":"f3546f4edc47daf7740500899b3892c9a78e3169","tid":2408465,"uid":231724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285e2c1357e32418c18ceddee179a041569b8929","tid":2408465,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2373167147ab6da9d7d3bf301dd803ba04d94542","tid":2408465,"uid":144453,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T03:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yBoFwvg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyBoFwvg.gif&h=8cbdf0bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-